snippet: At the Insight Bowl in Tempe, Ariz., on Friday night, an overhead remote-controlled camera fell to the field late in the fourth quarter, nearly hitting one of the players.
lead_paragraph: At the Insight Bowl in Tempe, Ariz., on Friday night, an overhead remote-controlled camera fell to the field late in the fourth quarter, nearly hitting one of the players.
